1
00:00:02,531 --> 00:00:06,567
[Goswami Mj]: Even remote contact
with a very powerful virus

2
00:00:06,567 --> 00:00:07,929
can infect someone.

3
00:00:08,239 --> 00:00:12,560
[Spiritual Virus | Die to Live]

4
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:15,950
A microscopic amount
of some substance

5
00:00:15,950 --> 00:00:20,404
can enter your system
and completely alter you,

6
00:00:20,498 --> 00:00:22,811
bring you to the stage
of mortality.

7
00:00:22,811 --> 00:00:26,319
[The “Inception” movie]:
What’s the most resilient parasite?

8
00:00:26,319 --> 00:00:31,749
A bacteria? A virus?
An idea.

9
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:35,274
Resilient, highly contagious.

10
00:00:35,294 --> 00:00:39,584
Once an idea’s taken hold of the brain,
it’s almost impossible to eradicate,

11
00:00:39,584 --> 00:00:43,454
but an idea that’s fully formed, 
fully understood—that sticks.

12
00:00:43,604 --> 00:00:47,658
Some microscopic amount 
of spiritual substance

13
00:00:47,658 --> 00:00:51,689
can enter within you 
and take you to the immortal plane.

14
00:00:51,689 --> 00:00:54,571
[V. Storaro]: The idea—
it doesn’t matter if you do them

15
00:00:54,571 --> 00:01:01,551
on stone, on wood, on canvas,
on films or in electronic—

16
00:01:01,551 --> 00:01:05,830
the idea is the one 
that really stays, always.

17
00:01:05,830 --> 00:01:11,260
And it’s a fact—everyone who hears 
even a minuscule amount of hari-kathā,

18
00:01:11,260 --> 00:01:14,220
or something about Kṛṣṇa,

19
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:15,890
becomes infected.

20
00:01:16,180 --> 00:01:18,731
And then the virus 
enters the system

21
00:01:18,731 --> 00:01:22,353
and expresses itself in time

22
00:01:22,353 --> 00:01:25,193
until it takes over 
the whole system.

23
00:01:25,193 --> 00:01:27,877
[G. Willis]: 
It’s the idea that is important.

24
00:01:27,877 --> 00:01:32,497
It’s why you do something as opposed 
to how you do something.

25
00:01:32,497 --> 00:01:35,044
What you do, 
and why you do it.

26
00:01:35,044 --> 00:01:37,599
Die to live.

27
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:42,229
Finish with one body, 
and the spiritual form begins to manifest.

28
00:01:42,378 --> 00:01:44,958
That’s a wonderful thing!

